Subject: [PATCH] mmc: block: Disable CMDQ on the ioctl path
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 70b52f09080565030a530a784f1c9948a7f48ca3
